<paragraph id="IFRS07_4"><paranum>4</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 7"/><data name="paranum" value="4"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS07_P0061">This IFRS applies to recognised and unrecognised <xref base="SL37522960" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0110">financial instruments<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0126"/></ph></xref>. Recognised financial instruments include <xref base="SL37522973" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0115">financial assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0123"/></ph></xref> and <xref base="SL37523036" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0131">financial liabilities<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0127"/></ph></xref> that are within the <xref base="F71835180" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_g2.1-2.7.dita#IFRS09_g2.1-2.7/IFRS09_g2.1-2.7_TI" id="IFRS07_X0153">scope of IFRS 9</xref>. Unrecognised financial instruments include some financial instruments that, although outside the scope of IFRS 9, are within the scope of this IFRS.</p></body></paragraph>